---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 sm:py-12">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16 sm:mb-24">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        Born from Flame,<br />
        <span class="text-gold italic">Made by Hand</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Bayou Bazaar started as a kitchen-table hobby and grew into a small-batch candle brand rooted in South Louisiana tradition.
        Every candle we pour carries a piece of this place.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Story Sections -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 mb-16 sm:mb-24">
      <div>
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🕯️</div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The Pour</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Every candle at Bayou Bazaar is hand-poured in small batches — no assembly lines, no shortcuts.
          We work with premium soy wax and pure beeswax, blended to a careful ratio that gives each candle
          a clean, even burn from the first light to the last.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          We use natural cotton wicks and carefully measured fragrance oils to ensure a strong, true-to-scent
          throw without the harshness of synthetic additives. Each jar is filled by hand, cooled slowly,
          and trimmed before it ever ships.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌿</div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The Scents</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Our fragrance palette is rooted in the sights, sounds, and smells of South Louisiana — magnolia
          blossoms in late spring, cypress trees draped in Spanish moss, sweet olive drifting through open
          windows, and the soft vanilla warmth of a bayou evening.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          We develop every scent in-house, testing dozens of blends before settling on the ones that feel
          genuinely alive. If it doesn't smell like something you'd find here, it doesn't make the collection.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-bayou-card border border-bayou-border rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 mb-16 sm:mb-24">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🫙</div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Why Jar Candles?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Jar candles are our heart and soul. They burn cleaner than open pillars, hold their fragrance
          longer, and the glass vessel protects the wax as it melts — meaning a more even pool, better
          scent throw, and less wasted wax.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          When the candle is done, the jar lives on. Rinse it out and use it for pens, cotton balls, herbs
          from your garden, or just leave it on the shelf as a pretty keepsake. They also make the most
          beautiful gifts — we wrap every order with care so it's ready for someone special.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Values -->
    <div class="mb-16 sm:mb-24">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-12">Our Values</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
        {[
          { icon: '🫙', title: 'Small-Batch', desc: 'We pour in small runs so every candle gets the attention it deserves. No bulk shortcuts.' },
          { icon: '🌿', title: 'Natural Ingredients', desc: 'Soy wax, beeswax, cotton wicks, and premium fragrance oils. Nothing synthetic, nothing harsh.' },
          { icon: '⚜️', title: 'Louisiana Made', desc: 'Poured right here in South Louisiana. Every scent, every label, every candle — born in the bayou.' },
          { icon: '🕯️', title: 'Hand-Poured', desc: 'Every single candle is poured by hand. That\'s not a marketing line — it\'s just how we work.' },
          { icon: '🎁', title: 'Gifting Friendly', desc: 'Beautiful packaging, long shelf life, and universal appeal make our candles perfect gifts for anyone.' },
          { icon: '⏱️', title: 'Long Burn Time', desc: 'Our jar candles burn 40-60+ hours. We test every formula so you get the most from every pour.' },
        ].map(v => (
          <div class="bg-bayou-card border border-bayou-border rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-gold/30 transition-colors">
            <span class="text-2xl mb-3 block">{v.icon}</span>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-white font-semibold mb-2">{v.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">{v.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Find Your Scent?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Browse our full collection of hand-poured soy, beeswax, and blended candles — each one made with love in South Louisiana.
      </p>
      <a href="/shop" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3.5 bg-gold text-bayou-black font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-gold-light transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-gold/20">
        Shop the Collection
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
